Package org.jets3t.service.multithread

Interface Summary
CancelEventTrigger Interface implemented by multi-threaded S3 operations that can be cancelled prior to finishing.
S3ServiceEventListener Listener for events produced by S3ServiceMulti.

DownloadPackage A simple container object to associate an S3Object with an output file, where the object's data will be written to.
